transArray.content: The surrounding environment is very inconvenient! If it is not for special reasons, don't live here. In addition to the indoor environment is OK, the surroundings are simply troublesome! You are not allowed to walk here, and you are not allowed to pass there. If you stop the car, you will be called in a series of fatal calls to prevent you from parking on the side of the road, but you are not qualified to park in the surrounding underground parking garages!
